Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.92,0:00:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到能遇上你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處女座的我  不得不感慨傷感的命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說  是因為沒有釋放光粒子  才被發現的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是後者吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被完全壓制了！不過！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣的龐然大物可打不中我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一塊裝甲碎片歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是光束軍刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公元2307年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立武裝組織  Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣言要根除全世界戰爭的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並開始進行武裝干預
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干預了印度南部錫蘭島的民族紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而震驚世界的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:02:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到了新的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是神對於人類的制裁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是  變革的序曲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:13.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}#03 變化的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  你真是個無法預測的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了來福槍  又得寫檢討了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心這個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次戰鬥所獲得的Gundam的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使損失了一台Flag  也是賺的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑藉和他接觸時弄上去的塗料  也許能夠追蹤到他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  還真年輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他對話了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的動作裡蘊含著感情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam  追蹤失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單獨出擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Flag  到底是什麼來頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和現場特派員聯絡上了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是Gundam啊  小點也沒關係  把畫像先放進去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being沒有進行聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  十分鐘以內開始播放特別報道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一條新聞是現場直播
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:18.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾小時內  人革主席將會發表官方聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把版面空出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稿子做出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…絹江…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是21世紀後期出現的絕無僅有的發明之王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倡導了太陽光發電系統的基礎理論
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但從來不抛頭露面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他的大名流傳後世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是他創建了Celestial Being的話  還是可信的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是才能還是資金方面…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  為什麼200多年以後的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們才開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·修亨伯格家族的血緣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他那一代完全斷絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:08.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}AEU  諜報機關本部  長官室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的資產流向了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時的記錄裡什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是故意做了手腳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21世紀的情報安全系統可是擺設一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being他們做得很周全  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官您認為他們的武力干預會一直繼續下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果換成是我  一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我把議會報告用的資料做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉口也幫我找好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:38.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,0)}人革聯  軌道電梯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天柱交通公司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭乘E273號班次的旅客們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在A12號門集合  謝謝您的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  遲到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個好勝的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經向吠陀上交了報告書
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會我會看一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都沒事比什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙那邊就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去執行下一個任務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會遵從命令的  雖然有不定因素
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  真的做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用軌道電梯把機體送回宇宙這樣的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照原計劃  把它們混進了殖民地開發用的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重量一樣  只要能搬進去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後的檢查就沒什麼問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是在這個地方進行檢查的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個盲點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們如果說有弱點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是沒有Gundam就會像普特利麥奧斯一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動時間被限制到了極點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有區區四個太陽爐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機密情報不要說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞的列車到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天柱交通公司的E277班次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將於預定時刻  14點18分…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連向宇宙的直線通道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭地面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望能稍微休息一會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁熱打鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一兩次的話  世界可是不會認同我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候已久  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有重力的地方真是舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很能體會您的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  司令正在等著  請跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前我想到錫蘭去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是只相信親眼所見的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令也應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我陪您前往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:16.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,300)}聯合  MSWAD總部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該是AEU新機型的發佈會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果發生了不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然存在那樣的機體  真是難以想像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得非常有研究價值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高層也是這樣認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給親眼看到Gundam的你們兩個下達了調職命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「對Gundam調查隊」…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新設立的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式名稱之後將由司令部命名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷夫·埃夫曼教授…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他來擔任技術主任嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高層就是這麼重視這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘快給我搞定它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆·艾卡中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利·片桐技術顧問
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受對Gundam調查隊的調職命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經預見到這樣的事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒那麼大的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得這就是緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛爾蘭的阿爾斯特地區
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是零散的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但恐怖行動持續了將近4世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Catholic Protestant{\fsp225}　{\r}\N雖說是天主教和新教的基督教兩個派別對立而引起的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩派的矛盾似乎還遠不止於此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的論文就以北愛爾蘭的對立為主題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是論文啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是工學部  為什麼要有歷史課
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「之後的技術革命將以軌道電梯的維持和太空殖民地開發為中心」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「以與各國技術者的交流為目的  培養歷史觀也是有必要的」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始沒說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然能夠理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  託這個福  我才能留學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點倒是很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年後  留學生活也就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  沙慈考慮過將來的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不確定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有把我考慮進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不確定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一會  路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的時候應該追上來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只點了軟飲料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的推薦可是原味雞尾酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可還沒成年哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上第三個任務就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要看的話  建議您準備3個顯示器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那還真是期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在偷窺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:44.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,300)}錫蘭島內\N人革聯  駐軍基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊請  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  有搞清楚什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是謝爾蓋中校  請說明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是MS的爆擊用功能組件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,材質是E Carbon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是最新的原材料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在結構上並未確認有新技術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那所搭載的導彈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  通過調查殘留物得知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是300km左右的制導導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外  沒有開發此類型的國家和製造商
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是獨自開發的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從機體所受的衝擊度來看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的輸出功率有Flag的6倍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底裝了什麼馬達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是那種輸出功率  還有那機動性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用戰鬥資料確認過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現那種機動性的果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  從Gundam的機體釋放出類似發光粒子的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可算是令人信服的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:13:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被雷達和傳感器探測到  是因為這個原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種特殊粒子除了用於隱形外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用於機體控制
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕還能用於武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷夫·埃夫曼教授
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個可怕的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有比我們先進幾十年的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在Celestial Being的罪行聲明中露面的歷史人物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是太陽光發電系統的倡導者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諜報部好像在根據這一線索來追查Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好驕傲的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個組件也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來不錯的技術在使用中被拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能辦到的話  真想捕獲到它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那稱作Gundam的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此  想拜託調試一下這個機體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那對機師的負擔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不用考慮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  希望時限是一週
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真會亂講啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不稍微強行點的話  就無法吸引Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他完全被迷住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  Gundam出現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  有兩個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時行動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非洲南部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是對由礦物資源的開採權引起的內戰的武力干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:38.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}非洲南部地區  礦物資源開採現場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種欺淩弱小的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快解除武裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑了  逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一台是在塔利比亞  可以從這邊過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從心底裡討厭毒品等東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要燒掉的話  我希望能支持Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒品…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是要根除紛爭的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盤旋行動自開始已進行30分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:35.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}南美  塔利比亞上空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirios  現在開始作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標達成率為97%
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這種事  隨時都可以辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三台出現在這錫蘭島了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是第七駐地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以使用的鐵人還有嗎  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校親自去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的  我只相信親眼所見之事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三號機被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怪物嗎  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  繼續介入紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅逐目標
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊  射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一階段結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…Gundam嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟掉了槍械？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想試探我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我見識一下根絕戰爭什麼的覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要肉的話就給你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個頭部  歸我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達匯合點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已目測確認Virtue
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始返艦準備  相對引導系統工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運輸器  打開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯動系統良好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue  返艦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返艦完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue的GN驅動器  開始與普特利麥奧斯的連接操作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由Virtue向托勒密傳輸能量準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始傳輸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是宇宙好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來吧  乾下杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是免了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  行不通…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  你是旁邊房間的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫沙慈·克洛斯羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與姐姐兩個人在這房間一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也請多…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷淡啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  有工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近這陣子比較忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於Celestial Being的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯隨便吃點吧  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  沙慈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看新聞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了  看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天淩晨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北愛爾蘭的恐怖組織——真IRA正式發表宣稱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將基於武力的恐怖活動完全凍結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持續了400年的北愛爾蘭紛爭  實際上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並將開闢通向新的和平的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天作業的論文會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界  在改變…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用Celestial Being的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及利用該國的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.59,0:23:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Meister在奔赴充滿陰謀的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.58,0:23:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「對外交涉」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.70,0:23:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂政治  就如同變幻無窮的萬花筒


